author: jmes
description: Lua Obfuscator for Red-DiscordBot, features 5 different types of obfuscation for Roblox/FiveM scripts, requires lua5.1, nodejs16, and dotnet-runtime-6.0 to be installed on the system.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not persistently store data or metadata about users.
install_msg:
Thanks for installing

Set your obfuscator channel by typing [p]obfuscatorset channel <channelname>.
Enable private message/dm obfuscation for users with [p]obfuscatorset user @user]

**Make sure lua5.1, nodejs16 and dotnet-runtime-6.0 are installed on the system.**
name: Obfuscator
